  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Enhance health of 900 SaltPan Women in South India</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">14% of India&apos;s and 70% of Tamilnadu&apos;s Salt production is from Thoothukudi. It has lot of underground saline water, extracting salt from 1500 salt pans. There are more than 7000 women working. These women work from 7a.m to 4p.m under the hot sun. As a result they suffer from various health Hazards (Defects in eyes, skin &amp; wounds in feet). We will enhance the health conditions of selected workers through medical camps &amp; Trainings, Eye camps, Referral for eye surgery, Provision of protective gears.</narrative>
  </description>
